channel.title: Pur3zscape 525 HD conversion. Editted
channel.description:
Hello, my name is Hustle and I made a new source with tutorials on and in HD with alot of stuff editted from Pur3zscape By Ramsin. I made this hoping to see alot more 525s in HD and i'm tired of seeing barly editted 525s that are sourced from the original Pur3z. Enjoy!
Most of this was all copy/pasted from Ramsin's Pur3z release, because most of it's the same. Features High alch + low alch working Working Sounds Tele Block ~ [99%] Entangle ~ [90%] Clan Wars White Portal ~ [100%] Global Object Spawning ~ [100%] Split chat ~ [100%] Shoping main stock + player Stock ~ [95%] Server message every 60 seconds ~ [100%] ------------------- Magic with W/O Staff. ~ [75%] Blood barrage Shadow Barrage Smoke Barrage Ice Barrage Ice Burst Ice Blitz ------------------- Day mute ~ [100%] Hour Mute ~ [100%] Trading ~ [90%] Donater rank including yell ~ [100%] Bounty Hunter ~ [100%] Multi Pking ~ [100%] Working teletome ~ [100%] Working teleto ~ [100%] Working teleall ~ [100%] ------------------- Working ban ~ [100%] Working Mute ~ [100%] Working Kick ~ [100%] Working Unban ~ [100%] ------------------- Item On Item ~ [100%] Item On Objects ~ [100%] Magic On Item ~ [100%] ------------------- Edge PVP ~ [100%] Pk Points Gives random 1-5 ~ [100%] Good PVP drops ~ [100%] None spawnable items ~ [100%] Deaths Points ~ [100%] ------------------- Magic W/ Staff ~ [100%] Ice Barrage Blood Barrage Maismic Barrage AutoCast ~ [100%] ------------------- Working Veng + other lunar spells ~ [100%] Mage Bank ~ [100%] Banking ~ [100%] Deposit all ~ 78%] working emotes + skill Capes ~ [100%] Fixed Chat box ~ [100%] G maul Spec ~ [95%] Good Combat System ~ [85%] ------------------- Skills Mining ~ [95%] RuneCrafting ~ [95%] Fishing ~ [97%] WoodCutting ~ [93%] ------------------- New: More item on item added such as Anti-Dragonfire Shield to Draconic Visage. More maps. New starter. Custom Yell channel. (This is like the current Pur3zScape yell, you can make other colors with [URL=http://"http://www.colorschemer.com/online.html"]http://www.colorschemer.com/online.html[/URL]. Hp Bars were fixed. Took all existing text off GUI because it was annoying. Took abuseful commands out of CommandManager.Java, you can re-add them if you like, or code them as: [CODE]if(player.getUsername().equals("Hustle_NerDs")) {[/CODE] Redone the ENTIRE quest interface to make it look sweeter, unlike the Pur3z Boring one. (No offence, but if you see mine, you would probably agree.) Decreased Dragon Claws spec 30% Decreased alot of other specs to a more proper amount. I took Adze out, if you don't know why, don't ask. Due to HD, this is Cheat Client Proof. (It will null you if using Standard client) --------------- PICTURES Just to show Awesomeness [IMG]http://public.blu.livefilestore.com/y1pKEf07vTqmgqyUSpVovQ1_Qjb6XqvURAweizaQSGmfvH2un0VTcSSFGfU6bVFLeYFNITvCD1j0Ru2fOgF_VRu5g/ms1.png[/img]
More HD awesomeness, and me blaberin about claws spec [IMG]http://public.blu.livefilestore.com/y1p5RcY5jYPdNfniEjH8Z1DVRcADWF238ZeKlQWHQu_w36qfPN7_NtqLmku3UzmfRcfO8S6YnnM6X2FAlSBQluwSQ/ms2.png[/img]
